diff.comment: All the emoji IDs of the difficulty that the API returns.

diffStrength.comment: The emojis for the Difficulty Strength section of the API.

levelData.comment: The download, youtube, and workshop emojis. These are used for the buttons in the level info embed.

misc.comment: Currently, this only includes the question emoji, used for when the diffStrength is unknown.

diffColors.comment: All the difficulty colors for the level.
